Package com.github.aklakina.edmma.database.orms

Class FileData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.aklakina.edmma.database.orms.FileData
  • @Entity
public class FileData
extends java.lang.Object
    The FileData class represents a file in the database. It contains information about the name of the file, the last line read, and the last size of the file. It also contains methods to check if the file has changed, recalculate the size of the file, load the file, and get the file.
